casebody.data:
J.B., J.J., and D.D., Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
CITY OF HOBOKEN, Mayor Dawn Zimmer, Fire Chief Richard Blohm, Betty McLendon, Psy. D., and Comprehensive Psychological Services, P.A., Defendants-Respondents. C-322 September Term 2018
081048 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 16, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004440-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
